│ 1109-1114): Build the compare constant vector using undef values for unused   │
│ lanes instead of poison.\n  Reasoning: Comparing against poison operands      │
│ yields a poison result. Using undef avoids poisoning the entire compare       │
│ result vector; the unused lanes remain unconstrained.\n\n  Edit:\n  - Change: │
