│ PoisonValue::get(VecTy->getElementType()));`\n  - To: `SmallVector<Constant   │
│ *, 32> CmpC(VecTy->getNumElements(),                                          │
│ UndefValue::get(VecTy->getElementType()));`\n\n5. Conclusion:\nBy replacing   │
│ poison with undef in both the constant vector used for the vector compare and │
